 and reload the page, please.</b>\n    </div>\n</noscript>\n\n\n    \n\n    <div style=\"width:100%;\" id=\"content\"><div><div class=\"introduction\"><div class=\"container-fluid vertical-align\"><h1 class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\"><img src=\"https://www.oorep.com/assets/html/img/logo_small.png\" style=\"width:180px; height:65px;\" alt=\"OOREP - open online repertory of homeopathy\"></h1><div class=\"container text-center\"><ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\"><li class=\"nav-item\"><a class=\"nav-link active\" href=\"#tab_repertory\" id=\"tab_repertory_link\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Repertory</a></li><li class=\"nav-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"#MMView_tab_materia_medica\" id=\"MMView_tab_materia_medica_link\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Materia Medica</a></li></ul><div class=\"tab-content border-right border-left border-bottom\" id=\"divTabs_content\" style=\"padding:20px;\"><div class=\"tab-pane fade show active\" id=\"tab_repertory\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"ex1-tab-1\"><div class=\"container-fluid text-center\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-sm-12\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"dropdown col-md-2\" style=\"min-width:200px; margin-top:20px;\"><button type=\"button\" style=\"min-width: 195px;\" class=\"text-nowrap btn btn-block dropdown-toggle btn-secondary\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"repSelectionDropDownButton\">Repertory: publicum</button><div class=\"dropdown-menu\" id=\"repSelectionDropDown\"><a class=\"dropdown-item\" href=\"#\" data-value=\"boen\">boen - Therapeutic Pocketbook [todo]</a><a class=\"dropdown-item\" href=\"#\" data-value=\"boericke\">boericke - Pocket Manual</a><a class=\"dropdown-item\" href=\"#\" data-value=\"bogboen\">bogboen - Boenninghausen's Charact. and Rep.</a><a class=\"dropdown-item\" href=\"#\" data-value=\"boger\">boger - General Analysis</a><a class=\"dropdown-item\" href=\"#\" data-value=\"bogsk\">bogsk - Synoptic Key</a><a class=\"dropdown-item\" href=\"#\" data-value=\"bogsk-de\">bogsk-de - Synoptic Key [deutsch]</a><a class=\"dropdown-item\" href=\"#\" data-value=\"cowpert-de\">cowpert-de - Cowperthwaite's clinical idx. [deutsch]</a><a class=\"dropdown-item\" href=\"#\" data-value=\"dorcsi-de\">dorcsi-de - Symptomenverz. [deutsch]</a><a class=\"dropdown-item\" href=\"#\" data-value=\"hering\">hering - Hering's Guiding Symptoms</a><a class=\"dropdown-item\" href=\"#\" data-value=\"kent\">kent - Kent's Repertory</a><a class=\"dropdown-item\" href=\"#\" data-value=\"kent-de\">kent-de - Kents Repertorium [deutsch]</a><a class=\"dropdown-item\" href=\"#\" data-value=\"publicum\">publicum - Repertorium Publicum</a><a class=\"dropdown-item\" href=\"#\" data-value=\"robasif\">robasif - Sensations as if</a><a class=\"dropdown-item\" href=\"#\" data-value=\"tylercold\">tylercold - mini repertory of flu/cold</a></div></div><div class=\"col-sm\" style=\"margin-top:20px;\"><input class=\"form-control\" id=\"inputField\" placeholder=\"Enter a symptom (for example: head, pain, left)\"></div></div></div></div><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-sm-12\"><div class=\"row justify-content-center\"><div class=\"col-sm-10\" id=\"advancedSearchControlsDiv\"></div></div></div></div><div id=\"mainViewSearchButtons\" class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\" style=\"margin-top:20px;\"><button class=\"btn btn-primary text-nowrap\" style=\"width: 140px; margin: 5px;\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"oi oi-magnifying-glass\" title=\"Find\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span> Find</button><button id=\"buttonMainViewAdvancedSearch\" class=\"btn btn-secondary text-nowrap\" style=\"width: 140px; margin: 5px;\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"oi oi-cog\" title=\"Toggle options\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span> Advanced...</button></div><div class=\"container-fluid\" style=\"margin-top: 23px;\" id=\"resultStatus\"></div><div class=\"container-fluid\" id=\"resultDiv\"></div><div class=\"container-fluid\" id=\"repertoryView_paginationDiv\"></div></div></div><div class=\"tab-pane fade\" id=\"MMView_tab_materia_medica\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"ex1-tab-1\"><div class=\"container-fluid text-center\"><div class=\"row justify-content-center\"><div class=\"dropdown col-md-2\" style=\"min-width:200px; margin-top:20px;\" id=\"MMViewmmSelection_sdfjhsdljkhsdkjhsdjkhsdkjfhsdkfjhsdf\"><button type=\"button\" style=\"min-width: 195px;\" class=\"text-nowrap btn btn-block dropdown-toggle btn-secondary\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"MMViewmmSelectionDropDownButton\">M. Medica: clarke</button><div class=\"dropdown-menu\" id=\"MMViewmmSelectionDropDownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item\" href=\"#\">allen - Keynotes</a><a class=\"dropdown-item\" href=\"#\">allentf - Pure Materia Medica</a><a class=\"dropdown-item\" href=\"#\">boericke - Pocket Manual</a><a class=\"dropdown-item\" href=\"#\">bogsk - Synoptic Key</a><a class=\"dropdown-item\" href=\"#\">clarke - Practical Materia Medica</a><a class=\"dropdown-item\" href=\"#\">heringc - Condensed Materia Medica</a><a class=\"dropdown-item\" href=\"#\">heringc-de - Kurze Arzneimittel. [deutsch]</a></div></div><div class=\"col-sm\" style=\"margin-top:20px;\"><input class=\"form-control\" id=\"MMViewinputField\" placeholder=\"Enter some search terms (for example: menses, night)\"></div></div><div class=\"row justify-content-center\"><div class=\"col-sm-10\" id=\"MMView_advancedSearchControlsDiv\"></div></div><div id=\"MMView_mainViewSearchButtons\" class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\" style=\"margin-top:20px;\"><button class=\"btn btn-primary text-nowrap\" style=\"width: 140px; margin:5px;\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"oi oi-magnifying-glass\" title=\"Find\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span> Find</button><button id=\"MMView_buttonMainViewAdvancedSearch\" class=\"btn btn-secondary text-nowrap\" style=\"width: 140px; margin: 5px;\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"oi oi-cog\" title=\"Toggle options\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span> Advanced...</button></div><div id=\"MMView_resultStatusAlerts\" class=\"container-fluid\" style=\"margin-top:23px;\"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"span12\" id=\"theCaseDiv\"></div></div></div>\n\n    \n\n      <script async=\"\" id=\"main_script\" src=\"/assets/frontend-opt/main.js\"></script>\n\n      <div id=\"about\">\n\n          <div class=\"jumbotron jumbo-dark horizontal-center\" style=\"position: relative;\">\n            <div class=\"container\">\n              <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col align-self-center\">\n                  <div data-aos=\"fade-right\" data-aos-offset=\"200\" data-aos-easing=\"ease-in-sine\" data-aos-duration=\"600\" data-aos-once=\"true\" class=\"aos-init\">\n                    <div style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 10px\">\n\n                      <div class=\"d-sm-none\">\n                        <h3>\n                          <span>About</span>\n                        </h3>\n                      </div>\n\n                      <div class=\"d-none d-sm-block\">\n                        <h3>\n                          <span class=\"blue-dot\"></span>\n                          <span class=\"blue-dot\"></span>\n                          <span class=\"blue-dot\"></span>\n                          <span>About</span>\n                          <span class=\"blue-dot\"></span>\n                          <span class=\"blue-dot\"></span>\n                          <span class=\"blue-dot\"></span>\n                        </h3>\n                      </div>\n\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div style=\"text-align: justify; max-width:700px;\">\n                    <p>\n                      OOREP is an open online repertory for homeopathy.  It is open, because its source code is freely available,\n                      it is online, because a running instance of it is served right here on this very server for your convenience.\n                      It is NOT some kind of medical recommendation system - please read the disclaimer below.  Repertorisation is\n                      the looking up of homeopathic repertories (and materia medicas), and as such this system does not provide any\n                      information, which you cannot obtain from its original sources.  However, online repertorisation is so much\n                      more efficient than browsing through the printed books.\n                    </p>\n                    <p>\n                      A word from the author:\n                      OOREP was especially developed for people who study homeopathy, either professionally or as a hobby like I am.\n                      I am not making any money from developing this software or from a homeopathic practice of any sorts.  As an interested\n                      layperson I have found it difficult, if not impossible, to get access to a good electronic repertorisation.\n                      Most homeopathic softwares are very expensive and intended to be used by people who make money by using them.\n                      For those of us who don't (or don't yet), like hobbyists or students, the access to these kinds of programs used to be very slim.\n                      With OOREP I intend to improve this situation somewhat.  So I hope it is useful to others, too.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"col d-none d-sm-block\">\n                  <img height=\"500\" width=\"383\" src=\"https://www.oorep.com/assets/html/img/hahnemann_statue_2.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\">\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"jumbotron jumbo-light\" style=\"position: relative;\">\n            <div class=\"container\">\n              <div class=\"row h-100 text-center\">\n                <div class=\"col d-none d-sm-block\">\n                  <img src=\"https://www.oorep.com/assets/html/img/laptop-min.webp\" srcset=\"https://www.oorep.com/assets/html/img/laptop-min.webp 383w,\n                               https://www.oorep.com/assets/html/img/laptop-med.webp 500w,\n                               https://www.oorep.com/assets/html/img/laptop.webp 830w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 383px,\n                              (max-width: 1300px) 500px,\n                              830px\" style=\"position: relative; left:-15px;\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"OOREP screenshot\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"col my-auto\" style=\"font-size: 120%;\">\n                  <div class=\"text-center aos-init\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-aos=\"fade-left\" data-aos-delay=\"300\" data-aos-offset=\"200\" data-aos-easing=\"ease-in-sine\" data-aos-duration=\"600\" data-aos-once=\"true\">\n                    <div style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">\n                      <span class=\"oi oi-video\" style=\"font-size: 47px;\"></span>\n                    </div>\n                    <p>\n                      Short video tutorials to learn all about OOREP's features on\n                    </p>\n                    <p>\n                      <a href=\"https://vimeo.com/oorep\">\n                        <img src=\"https://www.oorep.com/assets/html/third-party/img/vimeo_logo_blue.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" height=\"47\" width=\"165\" alt=\"Vimeo logo\">\n                      </a>\n                    </p>\n                    <p>\n                      <small>\n                        (Also available on <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCcHQXsPwIK53ciSjR9_P2xw\">YouTube</a>)\n                      </small>\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n        </div>\n\n\n      <div class=\"jumbotron jumbo-dark horizontal-center background-image\" id=\"features\" style=\"position: relative;\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom: 10px\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\n          <div class=\"d-sm-none\">\n            <h3>\n              <span>Why use OOREP?</span>\n            </h3>\n<!--            hide on screens wider than sm-->\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"d-none d-sm-block\">\n            <h3>\n              <span class=\"white-dot\"></span>\n              <span class=\"white-dot\"></span>\n              <span class=\"white-dot\"></span>\n              <span>Why use OOREP?</span>\n              <span class=\"white-dot\"></span>\n              <span class=\"white-dot\"></span>\n              <span class=\"white-dot\"></span>\n            </h3>\n<!--            hide on screens smaller than md-->\n          </div>\n\n<!--          <div class=\"d-none d-sm-block\">-->\n<!--            <span class=\"white-dot\"></span>-->\n<!--            <span class=\"white-dot\"></span>-->\n<!--            <span class=\"white-dot\"></span>-->\n<!--          </div>-->\n<!--          <h3 style=\"display: inline;\">-->\n<!--            <span>Why use OOREP?</span>-->\n<!--          </h3>-->\n<!--          <div class=\"d-none d-sm-block\">-->\n<!--            <span class=\"white-dot\"></span>-->\n<!--            <span class=\"white-dot\"></span>-->\n<!--            <span class=\"white-dot\"></span>-->\n<!--          </div>-->\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-lg-4 col-sm-6\">\n          <div class=\"icon aos-init\" data-aos-delay=\"400\" data-aos=\"fade\" data-aos-offset=\"200\" data-aos-easing=\"ease-in-sine\" data-aos-duration=\"600\" data-aos-once=\"true\">\n            <img style=\"height:65px; width:55px;\" src=\"https://www.oorep.com/assets/html/img/icon-penguin.png\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"penguin\">\n          </div>\n          <h4>Powered by open-source</h4>\n          <p>Built using proven open-source technologies and products. You can also download all the source code and run your own version of the software.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-4 col-sm-6\">\n          <div class=\"icon aos-init\" data-aos-delay=\"400\" data-aos=\"fade\" data-aos-offset=\"200\" data-aos-easing=\"ease-in-sine\" data-aos-duration=\"600\" data-aos-once=\"true\">\n            <img style=\"height:55px; width:55px;\" src=\"https://www.oorep.com/assets/html/img/icon-browser.png\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"browser\">\n          </div>\n          <h4>Platform-independent</h4>\n          <p>Works with any computer and OS. All you need is a web-browser - no installations, serial numbers or dongles.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-4 col-sm-6\">\n          <div class=\"icon aos-init\" data-aos-delay=\"400\" data-aos=\"fade\" data-aos-offset=\"200\" data-aos-easing=\"ease-in-sine\" data-aos-duration=\"600\" data-aos-once=\"true\">\n            <img style=\"height:40px; width:50px;\" src=\"https://www.oorep.com/assets/html/img/icon-book.png\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"book\">\n          </div>\n          <h4>Various sources</h4>\n          <p>Search in well-known repertories and materia medicas like Kent, Boger, Hering, etc.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-4 col-sm-6\">\n          <div class=\"icon aos-init\" data-aos-delay=\"400\" data-aos=\"fade\" data-aos-offset=\"200\" data-aos-easing=\"ease-in-sine\" data-aos-duration=\"600\" data-aos-once=\"true\">\n            <img style=\"height:40px; width:40px;\" src=\"https://www.oorep.com/assets/html/img/icon-results.png\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"results\">\n          </div>\n          <h4>Get results fast</h4>\n          <p>Very easy to use: only the essential features - no distractions, no non-sense.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-4 col-sm-6\">\n          <div class=\"icon aos-init\" data-aos-delay=\"400\" data-aos=\"fade\" data-aos-offset=\"200\" data-aos-easing=\"ease-in-sine\" data-aos-duration=\"600\" data-aos-once=\"true\">\n            <img style=\"height:60px; width:60px;\" src=\"https://www.oorep.com/assets/html/img/icon-search.png\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"search\">\n          </div>\n          <h4>Advanced search</h4>\n          <p>Widen your search using wildcards, like <b>'cough*, dry*'</b>, or narrow it down using <b>'-'</b> (minus).</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-4 col-sm-6\">\n          <div class=\"icon aos-init\" data-aos-delay=\"400\" data-aos=\"fade\" data-aos-offset=\"200\" data-aos-easing=\"ease-in-sine\" data-aos-duration=\"600\" data-aos-once=\"true\">\n            <img style=\"height:55px; width:28px;\" src=\"https://www.oorep.com/assets/html/img/icon-mobile.png\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"mobile\">\n          </div>\n          <h4>Mobile friendly</h4>\n          <p>Although repertorisation requires screen real estate, OOREP's responsive design supports mobile devices.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n    \n\n    <div style=\"width:100%;\" id=\"content_bottom\">\n    <div id=\"disclaimer_div\" class=\"jumbotron jumbo-dark text-center center-block\" style=\"position: relative;\">\n\n        <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://github.com/nondeterministic/oorep\">\n            <img style=\"position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0; border: 0;\" src=\"https://www.oorep.com/assets/html/img/forkme_right_red_aa0000.png\" alt=\"Fork me on GitHub\">\n        </a>\n        <br>\n        <div class=\"container\" style=\"font-size:12px;\">\n            <h4 style=\"text-align:center; margin-bottom: 20px\">\n                <span>Hinweis <span class=\"white-dot\"></span> Disclaimer</span>\n            </h4>\n            <p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n                Diese Homöopathie-Website ist ausschließlich zu Informationszwecken gedacht.\n                Sie ist nicht geeignet zur Selbstmedikation oder ersetzt den Besuch eines Arztes oder Apothekers.\n                Die Wirksamkeit von Homöopathie ist wissenschaftlich nicht bewiesen!\n                Der Autor dieser Website übernimmt keine Verantwortung für die Richtigkeit der Ergebnisse oder die Folgen,\n                